name: Cherry and Polkda Dot Handbag
description:
Lookin’ for a bag with a rockabilly flair? This bag features teeny tiny cherrys with white polka dots on a black background. The inside is fully lined with black and white polka dot fabric!

	This handbag has a flap that measures 9.25”x5.25”. The bag itself measures 10”x8”. The straps are made out of heavy nylon webbing and measure 32.5”. The bag has a velcro closure.

	The handbag has thick interfacing so the bag keeps it shape and is more durable.

	The flap is reinforced with black nylon webbing on the back and is sewn into the sides of the handbag for durability.
